#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:2
msgid "流量相关"
msgstr "Traffic-Related Tools"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:5
msgid "TCPDump"
msgstr "TCPDump"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:6
msgid "TCPDump是一款数据包的抓取分析工具，可以将网络中传送的数据包的完全截获下来提供分析。它支持针对网络层、协议、主机、网络或端口的过滤，并提供逻辑语句来过滤包。"
msgstr "TCPDump is a packet capture and analysis tool that can capture packets transmitted over a network for analysis. It supports filtering by network layer, protocol, host, network, or port, and provides logical expressions for packet filtering."

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:9 ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:46
msgid "命令行常用选项"
msgstr "Common Command-Line Options"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:10
msgid "``-B <buffer_size>`` 抓取流量的缓冲区大小，若过小则可能丢包，单位为KB"
msgstr "``-B <buffer_size>`` Buffer size for captured traffic. If it is too small, packets may be dropped. Unit: KB"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:11
msgid "``-c <count>`` 抓取n个包后退出"
msgstr "``-c <count>`` Exit after capturing n packets"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:12
msgid "``-C <file_size>`` 当前记录的包超过一定大小后，另起一个文件记录，单位为MB"
msgstr "``-C <file_size>`` Start a new output file after the current packet file exceeds a given size. Unit: MB"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:13
msgid "``-i <interface>`` 指定抓取网卡经过的流量"
msgstr "``-i <interface>`` Specify the network interface to capture traffic from"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:14
msgid "``-n`` 不转换地址"
msgstr "``-n`` Do not resolve addresses"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:15
msgid "``-r <file>`` 读取保存的pcap文件"
msgstr "``-r <file>`` Read a saved pcap file"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:16
msgid "``-s <snaplen>`` 从每个报文中截取snaplen字节的数据，0为所有数据"
msgstr "``-s <snaplen>`` Capture snaplen bytes from each packet; 0 means all data"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:17
msgid "``-q`` 输出简略的协议相关信息，输出行都比较简短。"
msgstr "``-q`` Output brief protocol-related information with shorter lines."

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:18
msgid "``-W <cnt>`` 写满cnt个文件后就不再写入"
msgstr "``-W <cnt>`` Stop writing after cnt files are filled"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:19
msgid "``-w <file>`` 保存流量至文件"
msgstr "``-w <file>`` Save traffic to a file"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:20
#, python-format
msgid "按时间分包时，可使用strftime的格式命名，例如 ``%Y_%m_%d_%H_%M_%S.pcap``"
msgstr "When splitting packets by time, use strftime format strings for naming, for example ``%Y_%m_%d_%H_%M_%S.pcap``"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:21
msgid "``-G <seconds>`` 按时间分包"
msgstr "``-G <seconds>`` Split output by time"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:22
msgid "``-v`` 产生详细的输出，``-vv`` ``-vvv`` 会产生更详细的输出"
msgstr "``-v`` Produce verbose output; ``-vv`` and ``-vvv`` produce more detailed output"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:23
msgid "``-X`` 输出报文头和包的内容"
msgstr "``-X`` Output packet headers and packet contents"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:24
msgid "``-Z <user>`` 在写文件之前，转换用户"
msgstr "``-Z <user>`` Switch user before writing files"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:27
msgid "Bro"
msgstr "Bro"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:28
msgid "Bro是一个开源的网络流量分析工具，支持多种协议，可实时或者离线分析流量。"
msgstr "Bro is an open-source network traffic analysis tool that supports many protocols and can analyze traffic in real time or offline."

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:31
msgid "命令行"
msgstr "Command Line"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:32
msgid "实时监控 ``bro -i <interface> <list of script to load>``"
msgstr "Monitor in real time ``bro -i <interface> <list of script to load>``"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:33
msgid "分析本地流量 ``bro -r <pcapfile> <scripts...>``"
msgstr "Analyze local traffic ``bro -r <pcapfile> <scripts...>``"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:34
msgid "分割解析流量后的日志 ``bro-cut``"
msgstr "Split parsed traffic logs ``bro-cut``"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:37
msgid "脚本"
msgstr "Scripts"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:38
msgid "为了能够扩展和定制Bro的功能，Bro提供了一个事件驱动的脚本语言。"
msgstr "To extend and customize Bro, Bro provides an event-driven scripting language."

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:42
msgid "tcpflow"
msgstr "tcpflow"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:43
msgid "tcpflow也是一个抓包工具，它的特点是以流为单位显示数据内容，在分析HTTP等协议的数据时候，用tcpflow会更便捷。"
msgstr "tcpflow is also a packet capture tool. It displays data content by flow, which makes it more convenient when analyzing protocols such as HTTP."

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:47
msgid "``-b max_bytes`` 定义最大抓取流量"
msgstr "``-b max_bytes`` Define the maximum amount of captured traffic"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:48
msgid "``-e name`` 指定解析的scanner"
msgstr "``-e name`` Specify the scanner to use for parsing"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:49
msgid "``-i interface`` 指定抓取接口"
msgstr "``-i interface`` Specify the capture interface"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:50
msgid "``-o outputdir`` 指定输出文件夹"
msgstr "``-o outputdir`` Specify the output directory"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:51
msgid "``-r file`` 读取文件"
msgstr "``-r file`` Read a file"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:52
msgid "``-R file`` 读取文件，但是只读取完整的文件"
msgstr "``-R file`` Read a file, but only read complete files"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:55
msgid "tshark"
msgstr "tshark"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:56
msgid "WireShark的命令行工具，可以通过命令提取自己想要的数据，可以重定向到文件，也可以结合上层语言来调用命令行，实现对数据的处理。"
msgstr "The command-line tool for Wireshark. It can extract desired data through commands, redirect output to files, or be invoked from higher-level languages to process data."

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:59
msgid "输入接口"
msgstr "Input Interfaces"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:60
msgid "``-i <interface>`` 指定捕获接口，默认是第一个非本地循环接口"
msgstr "``-i <interface>`` Specify the capture interface. By default, the first non-loopback interface is used"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:61
msgid ""
"``-f <capture filter>`` "
"设置抓包过滤表达式，遵循libpcap过滤语法，这个选项在抓包的过程中过滤，如果是分析本地文件则用不到"
msgstr ""
"``-f <capture filter>`` "
"Set the capture filter expression using libpcap filter syntax. This option filters during capture and is not needed when analyzing a local file"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:62
msgid "``-s <snaplen>`` 设置快照长度，用来读取完整的数据包，因为网络中传输有65535的限制，值0代表快照长度65535，默认为65535"
msgstr "``-s <snaplen>`` Set the snapshot length used to read complete packets. Because network transmission has a 65535-byte limit, a value of 0 means a snapshot length of 65535. The default is 65535"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:63
msgid "``-p`` 以非混合模式工作，即只关心和本机有关的流量"
msgstr "``-p`` Work in non-promiscuous mode, meaning only traffic related to the local host is considered"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:64
msgid "``-B <buffer size>`` 设置缓冲区的大小，只对windows生效，默认是2M"
msgstr "``-B <buffer size>`` Set the buffer size. This only takes effect on Windows. The default is 2M"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:65
msgid "``-y <link type>`` 设置抓包的数据链路层协议，不设置则默认为 ``-L`` 找到的第一个协议"
msgstr "``-y <link type>`` Set the data-link layer protocol for capture. If unset, the first protocol found by ``-L`` is used by default"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:66
msgid "``-D`` 打印接口的列表并退出"
msgstr "``-D`` Print the interface list and exit"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:67
msgid "``-L`` 列出本机支持的数据链路层协议，供-y参数使用。"
msgstr "``-L`` List data-link layer protocols supported by the local host for use with the -y option."

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:68
msgid "``-r <infile>`` 设置读取本地文件"
msgstr "``-r <infile>`` Read a local file"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:71
msgid "捕获停止选项"
msgstr "Capture Stop Options"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:72
msgid "``-c <packet count>`` 捕获n个包之后结束，默认捕获无限个"
msgstr "``-c <packet count>`` Stop after capturing n packets. By default, capture indefinitely"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:73
msgid "``-a <autostop cond>``"
msgstr "``-a <autostop cond>``"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:74
msgid "``duration:NUM`` 在num秒之后停止捕获"
msgstr "``duration:NUM`` Stop capture after num seconds"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:75
msgid "``filesize:NUM`` 在numKB之后停止捕获"
msgstr "``filesize:NUM`` Stop capture after num KB"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:76
msgid "``files:NUM`` 在捕获num个文件之后停止捕获"
msgstr "``files:NUM`` Stop capture after num files"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:79
msgid "处理选项"
msgstr "Processing Options"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:80
msgid "``-Y <display filter>`` 使用读取过滤器的语法，在单次分析中可以代替 ``-R`` 选项"
msgstr "``-Y <display filter>`` Use display filter syntax. In one-pass analysis, this can replace the ``-R`` option"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:81
msgid "``-n`` 禁止所有地址名字解析（默认为允许所有）"
msgstr "``-n`` Disable all address name resolution (all resolution is enabled by default)"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:82
msgid ""
"``-N`` 启用某一层的地址名字解析。 ``m`` 代表MAC层， ``n`` 代表网络层， ``t`` 代表传输层， ``C`` "
"代表当前异步DNS查找。如果 ``-n`` 和 ``-N`` 参数同时存在， ``-n`` 将被忽略。如果 ``-n`` 和 ``-N`` "
"参数都不写，则默认打开所有地址名字解析。"
msgstr ""
"``-N`` Enable address name resolution for a given layer. ``m`` means the MAC layer, ``n`` means the network layer, ``t`` means the transport layer, and ``C`` "
"means concurrent asynchronous DNS lookup. If ``-n`` and ``-N`` are both present, ``-n`` is ignored. If neither ``-n`` nor ``-N`` "
"is specified, all address name resolution is enabled by default."

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:83
msgid ""
"``-d`` 将指定的数据按有关协议解包输出，如要将tcp 8888端口的流量按http解包，应该写为 ``-d "
"tcp.port==8888,http`` 。可用 ``tshark -d`` 列出所有支持的有效选择器。"
msgstr ""
"``-d`` Decode and output specified data according to a related protocol. For example, to decode traffic on TCP port 8888 as HTTP, write ``-d "
"tcp.port==8888,http``. Use ``tshark -d`` to list all supported valid selectors."

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:86
msgid "输出选项"
msgstr "Output Options"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:87
msgid "``-w <outfile>`` 设置raw数据的输出文件。不设置时为stdout"
msgstr "``-w <outfile>`` Set the output file for raw data. If unset, output goes to stdout"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:88
msgid ""
"``-F <output file type>`` 设置输出的文件格式，默认是 ``.pcapng``，使用 ``tshark -F`` "
"可列出所有支持的输出文件类型"
msgstr ""
"``-F <output file type>`` Set the output file format. The default is ``.pcapng``. Use ``tshark -F`` "
"to list all supported output file types"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:89
msgid "``-V`` 增加细节输出"
msgstr "``-V`` Increase output detail"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:90
msgid "``-O <protocols>`` 只显示此选项指定的协议的详细信息"
msgstr "``-O <protocols>`` Show detailed information only for the protocols specified by this option"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:91
msgid "``-P`` 即使将解码结果写入文件中，也打印包的概要信息"
msgstr "``-P`` Print packet summary information even when decoded results are written to a file"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:92
msgid "``-S <separator>`` 行分割符"
msgstr "``-S <separator>`` Line separator"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:93
msgid "``-x`` 设置在解码输出结果中，每个packet后面以HEX dump的方式显示具体数据"
msgstr "``-x`` In decoded output, show the concrete data after each packet as a HEX dump"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:94
msgid "``-T pdml|ps|text|fields|psml`` 设置解码结果输出的格式，默认为text"
msgstr "``-T pdml|ps|text|fields|psml`` Set the decoded output format. The default is text"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:95
msgid "``-e`` 如果 ``-T`` 选项指定， ``-e`` 用来指定输出哪些字段"
msgstr "``-e`` If the ``-T`` option is specified, ``-e`` selects which fields to output"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:96
msgid "``-t a|ad|d|dd|e|r|u|ud`` 设置解码结果的时间格式"
msgstr "``-t a|ad|d|dd|e|r|u|ud`` Set the time format for decoded output"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:97
msgid "``-u s|hms`` 格式化输出秒"
msgstr "``-u s|hms`` Format output seconds"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:98
msgid "``-l`` 在输出每个包之后flush标准输出"
msgstr "``-l`` Flush standard output after each packet is output"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:99
msgid "``-q`` 结合 ``-z`` 选项进行使用，来进行统计分析"
msgstr "``-q`` Use with the ``-z`` option for statistical analysis"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:100
msgid "``-X <key>:<value>`` 扩展项，lua_script、read_format"
msgstr "``-X <key>:<value>`` Extension options, such as lua_script and read_format"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:101
msgid "``-z`` 统计选项，具体的参考文档"
msgstr "``-z`` Statistics option. See the documentation for details"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:104
msgid "其他选项"
msgstr "Other Options"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:105
msgid "``-h`` 显示命令行帮助"
msgstr "``-h`` Show command-line help"

#: ../../source/manual/traffic.rst:106
msgid "``-v`` 显示tshark的版本信息"
msgstr "``-v`` Show tshark version information"
